# Local Node Instructions

This file is optional and machine-local.

- Copy to `node-instructions.local.md` on the current node if you want persona loads to include local node guidance.
- `node-instructions.local.md` is gitignored and must never contain secrets.
- `scripts/agent-instructions.sh` will append this file after the standard org/role/site/seat instruction stack.

## Example: JobHunter worker node

- This machine is the `dev-laptop` worker node for JobHunter execution.
- Primary project: `forseti-jobhunter-automation`.
- Primary seats on this node: `pm-jobhunter`, `dev-jobhunter`, `qa-jobhunter`.
- Do not perform master-node dispatch or project assignment from this machine.
- Do not claim commands for seats outside `NODE_ACTIVE_AGENTS`.
